			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Debug:\r\n1. CTRL+Shift+7\r\n2. Minsc->Recruit->Minsc & Boo Reunion\r\n3. Talk to Minsc\r\n\r\nLegitimate:\r\n1. Encounter Minsc in the Counting House and let him escape\r\n2. Encounter Minsc again in the Abandoned Cistern. Start combat with him and knock him out\r\n3. Start dialog with Minsc after knocking him out\r\n4. After the dialog help Minsc destroy the cracked walls in the Abandoned Cistern to find Boo\r\n5. Talk to Minsc"
				},
