					"type": 23,
					"value": "After being freed from the Absolute's thrall, Minsc tears his lair apart in the search for Boo. He eventually leads us to a small chamber that had been bricked up, and cautiously creeps in - warning us that it is the lair of a dangerous beast (Boo.)"
